h%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Du-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-c%E1%BB%91-s%C3%A0o/poem-VGRxHr1NDTY-jBxbWDsFkA">Thất đề - Du điểu tường cố sào - 失題－遊鳥翔故巢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-Ch%E1%BB%ADng/Th%C6%B0-%C4%90oan-Ch%C3%A2u-qu%E1%BA%ADn-trai-b%C3%ADch/poem-KVZDvpbWGvqbjnuMZNiPog">Thư Đoan Châu quận trai bích - 書端州郡齋壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-Ch%E1%BB%ADng/author-J6AHaNlkUxblXzifcyGwHQ">Bao Chửng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%A9-chi-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Nam/poem-RPzjJs8w7Mp-PjEw6EfMiQ">Tống Lương Tứ chi Quảng Nam - 送涼思之廣南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
